Prerequisites

- cmpi header files
  (The ones from sfcb are broken, you can use those below include/cmpi)
- a CIMOM (sfcb does nicely)
- SWIG 1.3.x (I used 1.3.35)
- Cmake (I used 2.4)
- Ruby ( ruby, ruby-devel)
- wbemcli (or any other way to access the CIMOM)

Now do:
 cd cmpi-bindings
 mkdir build
 cd build
 cmake ..
 make
 sudo make install
 sudo sfcbrepos -f
 sfcbd
	